 * @see https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_XML_and_HTML_character_entity_references#Predefined_entities_in_XML Wikipedia
 */
exports.XML_ENTITIES = freeze({amp:'&', apos:"'", gt:'>', lt:'<', quot:'"'})
